Name: Raptor Boost
Notes: once side b collides with a player, the punch hitbox starts, active frames 3-7, with 25 frames endlag

Name: Facon kick
Notes: strong hit frames 14-16, weaker hit frames 17-24, weakest hit frames 25-32

Name: Up Smash
Notes: active 21-22 and 27-28, first hit can do 8% or 14%, second hit can do 12%-13%

Name: Falcon Dive
Notes: can grab ledge 5 frames after active end. if grabbed, hit is active frames 2-6 and hit animation takes a total of 79 frames

Name: Falcon Kick (Air)
Notes: can also do 11% damage. landing lag only occurs if ground hitbox is activated, which is also the weak hitbox

Name: Raptor Boost (Air)

Notes: can grab ledge 5 frames after active end. if grabbed, hit is active frames 2-6 and hit animation takes a total of 79 frames
